channel.title: Faith-Pk V1
channel.description:
[size=14pt]This is my V1, yes i know it is delta, i didn't really care what server i coded on at the time i started this[/size]
~Uppit~ http://uppit.com/v/EKCM60EV
~Megaupload~ http://www.megaupload.com/?d=U9GNWRK6
REQUIRED TO HEAR SOUNDS!!
~Megaupload~ http://www.megaupload.com/?d=WZF3G62C
~Uppit~ http://uppit.com/v/hsmfpspn
Features
90% Weapon Sounds
Teleporting sounds for ancient, lunar, and modern magic
Some teleporting command sounds
Npc attacking sounds
All pk armors
Two different dragon platebodys, Dragon claws + spec hitting 4 times with random good hits
All godsword specs (not overpowered)
All Range weapons give range xp
All lunar spells except humidity
All ancient spells
Multi hit ice barrage
Pk following
Full Brimhaven Dungeon with fully working vines, stairs, logs, and stepping stones. (::bdungeon didnt want to make a portal - teleport for it)
Warriors Guild (find the command in client.java just do ctrl+f string command to find the command, should be near the top)
Not complete barbarian assault, ::interrole (if you have more then one in a role it will not work...)
New shops at ::kingsarea
Re-modeled ele' shirts, blouses, and legs
Working clan chat (except lootshare)
Kalphite Tunnels + Lair
TONS MORE BUT TOO TIRED TO TYPE THEM ALL
Dh Maxing Pics The max can range anywhere from 50-95! The lower the hp, the better!
